		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Ernst Haas</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about Ernst Haas, the photographer.  For Ernst B. Haas, the American political scientist, see <a href="/wiki/Ernst_B._Haas" title="Ernst B. Haas">Ernst B. Haas</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:242px;"><a href="/wiki/File:ErnstHaas.jpg" class="image" title="Cover of Ernst Haas' photo book, The Creation."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a8/ErnstHaas.jpg" width="240" height="156" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:ErnstHaas.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Cover of Ernst Haas' photo book, <i>The Creation</i>.</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Ernst Haas</b> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1921-03-02"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="03-02"><a href="/wiki/March_2" title="March 2">March 2</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1921" title="1921">1921</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1986-09-12"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-12"><a href="/wiki/September_12" title="September 12">September 12</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1986" title="1986">1986</a></span>) was an artist and influential <a href="/wiki/Photographer" title="Photographer">photographer</a> noted for his innovations in <a href="/wiki/Color_photography" title="Color photography">color photography</a>, experiments in abstract light and form, and as a member of the <a href="/wiki/Magnum_Photos" title="Magnum Photos">Magnum Photos</a> agency. The Estate of Ernst Haas is represented by <a href="/wiki/Bruce_Silverstein_Gallery" title="Bruce Silverstein Gallery">Bruce Silverstein Gallery</a> New York, NY.</p>
